To ensure the user's response has a maximum length of 50 characters, you can use a variable with the appropriate size as shown below:
```4gl
response = prompt 'Enter your name (maximum 50 characters): ';
if (length(response) > 50) then
    write 'Your entry is longer than 50 characters.';
end;
```

